# RushTracks portal build-time secrets (optional)
# Copy from repo root or set in CI

# TMDB API key for poster, genre, and rating enrichment at build time
# Get one at https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
TMDB_API_KEY=

# Gate secrets are Cloudflare Pages Worker secrets, not used at build time:
# RUSHTRACKS_GATE_SECRET, TRACKS_MASTER_PIN
# Cloudflare Pages Worker secrets for /api/availability (Available vs Request buttons):
# PLEX_SERVER_URL — Plex base URL reachable from Cloudflare (e.g. https://plex.yourdomain.com or NPM proxy)
# PLEX_TOKEN — Plex X-Plex-Token (Plex Web → item → View XML, or Settings → Network)
# Optional Jellyfin fallback: JELLYFIN_SERVER_URL, JELLYFIN_API_KEY
